<subSubSection pageId="46" pageNumber="530" type="discussion">
Specimens corresponding to 
<taxonomicName class="Mammalia" family="Phyllostomidae" genus="Lonchophylla" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="46" pageNumber="530" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="orienticollina">L. orienticollina</taxonomicName>
